          </div>
          <div class="finding">
            <div class="finding-icon bad">âœ•</div>
            <span>No structured entity data for AI to recognise your brand</span>
          </div>
          <div class="finding">
            <div class="finding-icon warn">âš </div>
            <span>Weak E-E-A-T signals â€” AI cannot verify your authority</span>
          </div>
          <div class="finding">
            <div class="finding-icon warn">âš </div>
            <span>No digital PR mentions AI models use as trust anchors</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- LEAD GATE -->
        <div class="gate" id="leadForm">
          <div class="gate-head">Get your full 12-point AI Visibility Report</div>
          <div class="gate-sub">
            See exactly <strong>what to fix first</strong> â€” a prioritised action plan sent to your inbox, free.
          </div>
          <div class="input-row">
            <input id="nameInput" placeholder="Your name" />
            <input id="emailInput" type="email" placeholder="Work email" />
          </div>
          <button class="gate-btn" onclick="submitLead()">Send my free report â†’</button>
          <div class="privacy">ðŸ”’ No spam. Unsubscribe any time.</div>
        </div>

        <!-- POST-GATE CTA -->
        <div class="fix-cta" id="fixCta">
          <div class="fix-cta-head">
            <strong>Report sent.</strong> While you wait â€” most businesses in your position fix this in under 30 days with the right system.
          </div>
          <a href="https://your-gumroad-link.com" class="cta-btn">
            Get the AI Visibility Playbook â€” $49 â†’
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /RESULT -->

  </div>
  <!-- /HERO -->

  <!-- STORY -->
  <section class="story reveal">
    <div class="story-label">The shift is already happening</div>
    <div class="story-statements">
      <div class="stmt lit">AI doesn't rank pages.</div>
      <div class="stmt lit">It <em>selects businesses</em> it trusts.</div>
      <div class="stmt lit">Your competitors are being chosen right now.</div>
      <div class="stmt lit">Most businesses <em>don't even know</em> they're invisible.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRODUCTS -->
  <section class="products reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Fix your visibility</div>
    <div class="prod-grid">

      <a href="https://your-gumroad-link.com" class="prod-card featured">
        <div class="prod-tag">Most Popular</div>
        <div class="prod-name">AI Visibility Playbook</div>
        <div class="prod-desc">The complete system to get your business cited and recommended by ChatGPT, Perplexity & Gemini. 47 pages, ready to implement.</div>
        <span class="prod-arrow">â†—</span>
      </a>

      <a href="https://your-gumroad-link.com/geo-blueprint" class="prod-card">
        <div class="prod-tag">Blueprint</div>
        <div class="prod-name">GEO-SEO Blueprint</div>
        <div class="prod-desc">Generative Engine Optimisation, step by step.</div>
        <span class="prod-arrow">â†—</span>
      </a>

      <a href="https://your-gumroad-link.com/n8n-workflow" class="prod-card">
